query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('serverfault')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('active-directory',
'amazon-ec2',
'apache-2.4',
'backup',
'centos',
'firewall',
'iis',
'iptables',
'security',
'ssh',
'windows-server-2003');
